{
  "stem": "17301.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then after that, they put me in public school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I went through public school in, in Uzhhorod We had, I had a lot of relatives there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I had my aunt, I had my, my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My grandfather died very, very, when I was a very young child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I had a lot of uncles, a lot of cousins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was a pretty large family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it was a pretty nice, prominent family at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the neighborhood was not strictly-- there was no such thing as a strictly Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had mostly Gentile neighbors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was brought up with, with a lot of Gentile people around me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a lot of Jewish girlfriends, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was a very mixed friendship with-- with all of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very beautiful friendship, very honest and very sincere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I never thought that we would come to what we did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had a very lovely young life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were not poor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to help in the house all the time, and we had a lovely home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother [BACKROUND NOISE] was a very loving, beautiful lady, that we had a lot of good times with, that we used to go Saturdays.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Our Saturdays outings were going and visiting my grandmother and the family, because that's what they did at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Later on, when I was in high school, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a little bit more difficult for me to get together with my, my friends because I had a lot of studying to do.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the schools were in the morning from 8 o'clock until 4 o'clock, and half day on Saturdays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a lot of studying to do, which I didn't mind because I enjoyed studying.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
